    if len(clocs) == 0:
        return data

    # NOTE: This doesn't deal with hierarchical columns yet

    index = data.index

    cloc_numbers = []
    for cloc in clocs:
        if isinstance(cloc, tuple):  # Handling tuple-multiindex
            cloc_number = []
            for clabel in cloc:  # Extracting labels from the tuple-multiindex
                cloc_number.append(index._get_level_number(clabel))
            cloc_numbers.append(cloc_number)
        else:
            cloc_numbers.append(index._get_level_number(cloc))

    rlocs = [i for i in range(index.nlevels) if i not in cloc_numbers]
